      <div class="gem-c-image-card gem-c-image-card--large ">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Read the New initiative to step up veterans article" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/69452/s712_DDC-20190307-066-004_copy.jpeg"></img></figure>

