        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link " href="/government/news/new-initiative-to-step-up-veterans-employment-in-the-automotive-sector">New initiative to step up veterans' employment in the automotive sector</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Major players from across the automotive industry, including Jaguar Land Rover and Westway Nissan, today launched a new initiative to help service leavers and veterans take up jobs in the sector motor industry.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


